{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Mountain biking in Israel"},{"time":4000,"text":"is something that I do with great passion"},{"time":6000,"text":"and commitment."},{"time":9000,"text":"And when I'm on my bike,"},{"time":11000,"text":"I feel that I connect"},{"time":13000,"text":"with the profound beauty of Israel,"},{"time":16000,"text":"and I feel that I'm united"},{"time":18000,"text":"with this country's history"},{"time":22000,"text":"and biblical law."},{"time":24000,"text":"And also, for me,"},{"time":26000,"text":"biking is a matter of empowerment."},{"time":28000,"text":"When I reach the summit"},{"time":30000,"text":"of a steep mountain in the middle of nowhere,"},{"time":32000,"text":"I feel young,"},{"time":34000,"text":"invincible, eternal."},{"time":37000,"text":"It's as if I'm connecting with some legacy"},{"time":40000,"text":"or with some energy"},{"time":42000,"text":"far greater than myself."},{"time":44000,"text":"You can see my fellow riders"},{"time":46000,"text":"at the end of the picture,"},{"time":48000,"text":"looking at me with some concern."},{"time":51000,"text":"And here is another picture of them."},{"time":53000,"text":"Unfortunately, I cannot show their faces,"},{"time":56000,"text":"neither can I disclose their true names,"},{"time":58000,"text":"and that's because my fellow riders"},{"time":60000,"text":"are juvenile inmates,"},{"time":62000,"text":"offenders"},{"time":64000,"text":"spending time in a correction facility"},{"time":66000,"text":"about 20 minutes' ride from here --"},{"time":69000,"text":"well, like everything in Israel."},{"time":73000,"text":"And I've been riding with these kids once a week,"},{"time":76000,"text":"every Tuesday, rain or shine, for the last four years"},{"time":79000,"text":"and by now, they've become a very big part of my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82000,"text":"This story began four years ago."},{"time":85000,"text":"The correction facility where they are locked up"},{"time":87000,"text":"happens to be right in the middle"},{"time":89000,"text":"of one of my usual trips,"},{"time":91000,"text":"and it's surrounded by barbed wires"},{"time":93000,"text":"and electric gates and armed guards."},{"time":95000,"text":"So on one of these rides,"},{"time":97000,"text":"I talked my way into the compound"},{"time":99000,"text":"and went to see the warden."},{"time":102000,"text":"I told the warden"},{"time":104000,"text":"that I wanted to start a mountain biking club in this place"},{"time":107000,"text":"and that basically I wanted to take the kids"},{"time":109000,"text":"from here to there."},{"time":112000,"text":"And I told him, \"Let's find a way"},{"time":114000,"text":"in which I'll be able to take out 10 kids once a week"},{"time":117000,"text":"to ride with in the summer in the country.\""},{"time":120000,"text":"And the warden was quite amused,"},{"time":122000,"text":"and he told me he thought that I was a nut"},{"time":125000,"text":"and he told me,"},{"time":127000,"text":"\"This place is a correction facility. These guys are serious offenders."},{"time":130000,"text":"They are supposed to be locked up."},{"time":132000,"text":"They aren't supposed to be out at large.\""},{"time":135000,"text":"And yet, we began to talk about it,"},{"time":137000,"text":"and one thing led to another."},{"time":139000,"text":"And I can't see myself"},{"time":142000,"text":"going into a state prison in New Jersey"},{"time":144000,"text":"and making such a proposition,"},{"time":146000,"text":"but this being Israel,"},{"time":148000,"text":"the warden somehow made it happen."},{"time":151000,"text":"And so two months later,"},{"time":154000,"text":"we found ourselves \"at large\" --"},{"time":156000,"text":"myself,"},{"time":158000,"text":"10 juvenile inmates"},{"time":161000,"text":"and a wonderful fellow named Russ,"},{"time":163000,"text":"who became a very good friend of mine"},{"time":165000,"text":"and my partner in this project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"And in the next few weeks, I had the tremendous pleasure"},{"time":170000,"text":"of introducing these kids"},{"time":172000,"text":"to the world of total freedom,"},{"time":174000,"text":"a world consisting of magnificent vistas"},{"time":177000,"text":"like these --"},{"time":179000,"text":"everything you see here is obviously in Israel --"},{"time":182000,"text":"as well as close encounters"},{"time":184000,"text":"with all sorts of small creatures"},{"time":186000,"text":"coming in all sorts of sizes,"},{"time":188000,"text":"colors, shapes, forms"},{"time":191000,"text":"and so on."},{"time":193000,"text":"In spite of all this splendor,"},{"time":196000,"text":"the beginning was extremely frustrating."},{"time":199000,"text":"Every small obstacle,"},{"time":201000,"text":"every slight uphill,"},{"time":203000,"text":"would cause these fellows"},{"time":205000,"text":"to stop in their tracks and give up."},{"time":208000,"text":"So we had a lot of this going on."},{"time":211000,"text":"I found out that they had a very hard time"},{"time":213000,"text":"dealing with frustration and difficulties --"},{"time":215000,"text":"not because they were physically unfit."},{"time":217000,"text":"But that's one reason why they ended up where they were."},{"time":221000,"text":"And I became increasingly more and more agitated,"},{"time":223000,"text":"because I was there"},{"time":225000,"text":"not only to be with them,"},{"time":227000,"text":"but also to ride and create a team"},{"time":229000,"text":"and I didn't know what to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"Now, let me give you an example."},{"time":233000,"text":"We're going downhill in some rocky terrain,"},{"time":236000,"text":"and the front tire of Alex"},{"time":239000,"text":"gets caught in one of these crevasses here."},{"time":241000,"text":"So he crashes down,"},{"time":243000,"text":"and he gets slightly injured,"},{"time":245000,"text":"but this does not prevent him from jumping up"},{"time":248000,"text":"and then starting to jump up and down on his bike"},{"time":250000,"text":"and curse violently."},{"time":252000,"text":"Then he throws his helmet in the air."},{"time":255000,"text":"His backpack goes ballistic in some other direction."},{"time":258000,"text":"And then he runs to the nearest tree"},{"time":260000,"text":"and starts to break branches and throw rocks"},{"time":263000,"text":"and curse like I've never heard."},{"time":266000,"text":"And I'm just standing there,"},{"time":269000,"text":"watching this scene"},{"time":271000,"text":"with a complete disbelief,"},{"time":273000,"text":"not knowing what to do."},{"time":276000,"text":"I'm used to algorithms"},{"time":278000,"text":"and data structures"},{"time":281000,"text":"and super motivated students,"},{"time":284000,"text":"and nothing in my background"},{"time":286000,"text":"prepared me to deal"},{"time":288000,"text":"with a raging, violent adolescent"},{"time":291000,"text":"in the middle of nowhere."},{"time":293000,"text":"And you have to realize that these incidents"},{"time":295000,"text":"did not happen in convenient locations."},{"time":297000,"text":"They happened in places like this,"},{"time":300000,"text":"in the Judean Desert,"},{"time":302000,"text":"20 kilometers away from the nearest road."},{"time":305000,"text":"And what you don't see in this picture"},{"time":307000,"text":"is that somewhere between these riders there,"},{"time":310000,"text":"there's a teenager sitting on a rock,"},{"time":312000,"text":"saying, \"I'm not moving from here. Forget it."},{"time":314000,"text":"I've had it.\""},{"time":316000,"text":"Well, that's a problem"},{"time":318000,"text":"because one way or another, you have to get this guy moving"},{"time":321000,"text":"because it's getting dark soon and dangerous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324000,"text":"It took me several such incidents to figure out what I was supposed to do."},{"time":327000,"text":"At the beginning, it was a disaster."},{"time":329000,"text":"I tried harsh words and threats"},{"time":331000,"text":"and they took me nowhere."},{"time":333000,"text":"That's what they had all their lives."},{"time":335000,"text":"And at some point I found out,"},{"time":338000,"text":"when a kid like this gets into a fit,"},{"time":340000,"text":"the best thing that you can possibly do"},{"time":342000,"text":"is stay as close as possible to this kid,"},{"time":345000,"text":"which is difficult,"},{"time":347000,"text":"because what you really want to do is go away."},{"time":349000,"text":"But that's what he had all his life,"},{"time":351000,"text":"people walking away from him."},{"time":353000,"text":"So what you have to do is stay close"},{"time":355000,"text":"and try to reach in"},{"time":357000,"text":"and pet his shoulder"},{"time":359000,"text":"or give him a piece of chocolate."},{"time":361000,"text":"So I would say, \"Alex, I know that it's terribly difficult."},{"time":364000,"text":"Why don't you rest for a few minutes"},{"time":366000,"text":"and then we'll go on.\""},{"time":368000,"text":"\"Go away you maniac-psychopath."},{"time":371000,"text":"Why would you bring us to this goddamn place?\""},{"time":375000,"text":"And I would say, \"Relax, Alex."},{"time":378000,"text":"Here's a piece of chocolate.\""},{"time":380000,"text":"And Alex would go, \"Arrrrggg!\""},{"time":382000,"text":"Because you have to understand"},{"time":384000,"text":"that on these rides we are constantly hungry --"},{"time":386000,"text":"and after the rides also."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390000,"text":"And who is this guy, Alex, to begin with?"},{"time":393000,"text":"He's a 17-year-old."},{"time":395000,"text":"When he was eight,"},{"time":397000,"text":"someone put him on a boat in Odessa"},{"time":400000,"text":"and sent him, shipped him to Israel"},{"time":403000,"text":"on his own."},{"time":405000,"text":"And he ended up in south Tel Aviv"},{"time":407000,"text":"and did not have the good luck"},{"time":409000,"text":"to be picked up by a [unclear]"},{"time":411000,"text":"and roamed the streets"},{"time":413000,"text":"and became a prominent gang member."},{"time":416000,"text":"And he spent the last 10 years of his life"},{"time":418000,"text":"in two places only,"},{"time":420000,"text":"the slums and the state prison,"},{"time":423000,"text":"where he spent the last two years"},{"time":425000,"text":"before he ended up sitting on this rock there."},{"time":428000,"text":"And so this kid"},{"time":430000,"text":"was probably abused,"},{"time":433000,"text":"abandoned, ignored, betrayed"},{"time":436000,"text":"by almost every adult along the way."},{"time":438000,"text":"So, for such a kid,"},{"time":440000,"text":"when an adult that he learns to respect stays close to him"},{"time":443000,"text":"and doesn't walk away from him"},{"time":445000,"text":"in any situation,"},{"time":447000,"text":"irrespective of how he behaves,"},{"time":450000,"text":"it's a tremendous healing experience."},{"time":453000,"text":"It's an act of unconditional acceptance,"},{"time":456000,"text":"something that he never had."}]},{"cues":[{"time":458000,"text":"I want to say a few words about vision."},{"time":460000,"text":"When I started this program four years ago,"},{"time":463000,"text":"I had this original plan"},{"time":466000,"text":"of creating a team"},{"time":468000,"text":"of winning underdogs."},{"time":470000,"text":"I had an image of Lance Armstrong"},{"time":473000,"text":"in my mind."},{"time":475000,"text":"And it took me exactly two months"},{"time":478000,"text":"of complete frustration"},{"time":480000,"text":"to realize that this vision"},{"time":482000,"text":"was misplaced,"},{"time":484000,"text":"and that there was another vision"},{"time":486000,"text":"supremely more important"},{"time":488000,"text":"and more readily available."},{"time":491000,"text":"It all of a sudden dawned on me, in this project,"},{"time":494000,"text":"that the purpose of these rides"},{"time":496000,"text":"should actually be"},{"time":498000,"text":"to expose the kids"},{"time":500000,"text":"to one thing only: love."},{"time":503000,"text":"Love to the country, to the uphill"},{"time":505000,"text":"and the downhill,"},{"time":507000,"text":"to all the incredible creatures that surround us --"},{"time":510000,"text":"the animals, the plants,"},{"time":512000,"text":"the insects --"},{"time":514000,"text":"love and respect"},{"time":516000,"text":"to other fellow members in your team,"},{"time":518000,"text":"in your biking team,"},{"time":520000,"text":"and most importantly,"},{"time":522000,"text":"love and respect to yourself,"},{"time":524000,"text":"which is something"},{"time":526000,"text":"that they badly miss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528000,"text":"Together with the kids,"},{"time":530000,"text":"I also went through a remarkable transformation."},{"time":533000,"text":"Now, I come from a cutthroat world"},{"time":535000,"text":"of science and high technology."},{"time":537000,"text":"I used to think that reason and logic"},{"time":540000,"text":"and relentless drive"},{"time":542000,"text":"were the only ways to make things happen."},{"time":544000,"text":"And before I worked with the kids,"},{"time":546000,"text":"anything that I did with them,"},{"time":548000,"text":"or anything that I did with myself,"},{"time":550000,"text":"was supposed to be perfect,"},{"time":552000,"text":"ideal, optimal,"},{"time":555000,"text":"but after working with them for some time,"},{"time":559000,"text":"I discovered the great virtues of empathy"},{"time":562000,"text":"and flexibility"},{"time":564000,"text":"and being able to start with some vision,"},{"time":566000,"text":"and if the vision doesn't work, well nothing happened."},{"time":569000,"text":"All you have to do is play with it, change it a little bit,"},{"time":572000,"text":"and come up with something that does help, that does work."},{"time":575000,"text":"So right now, I feel more"},{"time":577000,"text":"like these are my principles,"},{"time":579000,"text":"and if you don't like them,"},{"time":581000,"text":"I have others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":585000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"And one of these principles"},{"time":592000,"text":"is focus."},{"time":594000,"text":"Before each ride"},{"time":596000,"text":"we sit together with the kids,"},{"time":598000,"text":"and we give them one word"},{"time":600000,"text":"to think about during the ride."},{"time":602000,"text":"You have to focus their attention on something"},{"time":605000,"text":"because so many things happen."},{"time":607000,"text":"So these are words like \"teamwork\""},{"time":609000,"text":"or \"endurance\""},{"time":611000,"text":"or even complicated concepts"},{"time":613000,"text":"like \"resource allocation\""},{"time":615000,"text":"or \"perspective,\" a word that they don't understand."},{"time":617000,"text":"You know, perspective"},{"time":619000,"text":"is one of these critically important"},{"time":621000,"text":"life-coping strategies"},{"time":623000,"text":"that mountain biking can really teach you."},{"time":626000,"text":"I tell kids"},{"time":628000,"text":"when they struggle through some uphill"},{"time":631000,"text":"and feel like they cannot take it anymore,"},{"time":633000,"text":"it really helps to ignore the immediate obstacles"},{"time":636000,"text":"and raise your head and look around"},{"time":638000,"text":"and see how the vista around you grows."},{"time":640000,"text":"It literally propels you upwards."},{"time":643000,"text":"That's what perspective is all about."},{"time":645000,"text":"Or you can also look back in time"},{"time":647000,"text":"and realize that you've already conquered"},{"time":649000,"text":"steeper mountains before."},{"time":652000,"text":"And that's how they develop self-esteem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655000,"text":"Now, let me give you an example of how it works."},{"time":657000,"text":"You stand with your bike at the beginning of February."},{"time":660000,"text":"It's very cold, and you're standing in one of these rainy days,"},{"time":663000,"text":"and it's drizzling"},{"time":665000,"text":"and cold and chilly,"},{"time":668000,"text":"and you're standing in, let's say, Yokneam."},{"time":671000,"text":"And you look up at the sky through a hole in the clouds"},{"time":674000,"text":"you see the monastery at the top of the Muhraka --"},{"time":677000,"text":"that's where you're supposed to climb now --"},{"time":679000,"text":"and you say, \"There's no way that I could possibly get there.\""},{"time":682000,"text":"And yet, two hours later"},{"time":685000,"text":"you find yourself standing on the roof of this monastery,"},{"time":688000,"text":"smeared with mud,"},{"time":691000,"text":"blood and sweat."},{"time":693000,"text":"And you look down at Yokneam;"},{"time":695000,"text":"everything is so small and tiny."},{"time":697000,"text":"And you say, \"Hey, Alex. Look at this parking lot where we started."},{"time":699000,"text":"It's that big."},{"time":701000,"text":"I can't believe that I did it.\""},{"time":703000,"text":"And that's the point"},{"time":705000,"text":"when you start loving yourself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":708000,"text":"And so we talked about"},{"time":710000,"text":"these special words that we teach them."},{"time":712000,"text":"And at the end of each ride, we sit together"},{"time":715000,"text":"and share moments"},{"time":717000,"text":"in which those special words of the day"},{"time":720000,"text":"popped up and made a difference,"},{"time":722000,"text":"and these discussions"},{"time":724000,"text":"can be extremely inspiring."},{"time":726000,"text":"In one of them, one of the kids once said,"},{"time":728000,"text":"\"When we were riding on this ridge"},{"time":730000,"text":"overlooking the Dead Sea --"},{"time":732000,"text":"and he's talking about this spot here --"},{"time":735000,"text":"\"I was reminded"},{"time":737000,"text":"of the day when I left my village in Ethiopia"},{"time":739000,"text":"and went away together with my brother."},{"time":742000,"text":"We walked 120 kilometers"},{"time":744000,"text":"until we reached Sudan."},{"time":746000,"text":"This was the first place where we got some water and supplies.\""},{"time":749000,"text":"And he goes on saying, and everyone looks at him like a hero,"},{"time":752000,"text":"probably for the first time in his life."},{"time":754000,"text":"And he says -- because I also have volunteers riding with me,"},{"time":757000,"text":"adults, who are sitting there"},{"time":759000,"text":"listening to him --"},{"time":762000,"text":"and he says, \"And this was just the beginning"},{"time":764000,"text":"of our ordeal"},{"time":766000,"text":"until we ended up in Israel."},{"time":768000,"text":"And only now,\" he says,"},{"time":770000,"text":"\"I'm beginning to understand where I am,"},{"time":772000,"text":"and I actually like it.\""},{"time":774000,"text":"Now I remember, when he said it,"},{"time":776000,"text":"I felt goosebumps on my body,"},{"time":778000,"text":"because he said it overlooking the Moab Mountains here in the background."},{"time":781000,"text":"That's where Joshua descended"},{"time":783000,"text":"and crossed the Jordan"},{"time":785000,"text":"and led the people of Israel into the land of Canaan"},{"time":788000,"text":"3,000 years ago"},{"time":790000,"text":"in this final leg"},{"time":792000,"text":"of the journey from Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":795000,"text":"And so, perspective"},{"time":797000,"text":"and context and history"},{"time":799000,"text":"play key roles"},{"time":801000,"text":"in the way I plan my rides"},{"time":803000,"text":"with the kids."},{"time":805000,"text":"We visit Kibbutzim"},{"time":807000,"text":"that were established by Holocaust survivors."},{"time":810000,"text":"We explore ruins"},{"time":813000,"text":"of Palestinian villages,"},{"time":816000,"text":"and we discuss how they became ruins."},{"time":819000,"text":"And we go through numerous remnants"},{"time":822000,"text":"of Jewish settlements, Nabatic settlements,"},{"time":824000,"text":"Canaanite settlements --"},{"time":826000,"text":"three-, four, five-thousand years old."},{"time":828000,"text":"And through this tapestry,"},{"time":830000,"text":"which is the history of this country,"},{"time":833000,"text":"the kids acquire"},{"time":835000,"text":"what is probably the most important"},{"time":837000,"text":"value in education,"},{"time":839000,"text":"and that is the understanding that life is complex,"},{"time":843000,"text":"and there's no black and white."},{"time":846000,"text":"And by appreciating complexity,"},{"time":848000,"text":"they become more tolerant,"},{"time":850000,"text":"and tolerance leads to hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":854000,"text":"I ride with these kids once a week,"},{"time":856000,"text":"every Tuesday."},{"time":858000,"text":"Here's a picture I took last Tuesday -- less than a week ago --"},{"time":861000,"text":"and I ride with them tomorrow also."},{"time":863000,"text":"In every one of these rides"},{"time":866000,"text":"I always end up standing in one of these incredible locations,"},{"time":869000,"text":"taking in this incredible landscape around me,"},{"time":872000,"text":"and I feel blessed and fortunate"},{"time":874000,"text":"that I'm alive,"},{"time":876000,"text":"and that I sense every fiber"},{"time":878000,"text":"in my aching body."},{"time":880000,"text":"And I feel blessed and fortunate"},{"time":882000,"text":"that 15 years ago"},{"time":884000,"text":"I had the courage to resign"},{"time":886000,"text":"my tenured position at NYU"},{"time":888000,"text":"and return to my home country"},{"time":890000,"text":"where I can do these incredible rides"},{"time":892000,"text":"with this group of troubled kids"},{"time":894000,"text":"coming from Ethiopia"},{"time":896000,"text":"and Morocco and Russia."},{"time":899000,"text":"And I feel blessed and fortunate"},{"time":901000,"text":"that every week, every Tuesday --"},{"time":903000,"text":"and actually every Friday also --"},{"time":906000,"text":"I can once again celebrate"},{"time":909000,"text":"in the marrow of my bones"},{"time":912000,"text":"the very essence of living in Israel on the edge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":915000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":917000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}